### 0.6 What's Missing

A bunch of features are missing, mostly because my coding time is limited. If you want to see these features implemented, either add them yourself or give me a grant.

* _Continuous Collision Detection (CCD)_ and _Global Intersection Analysis (GIA)_: If something weird happens under violent collisions, e.g. triangles get snagged, this is probably why.
* _Line Search_: If the simulation explodes, this is probably why.
* _Shells and Strands_: For now, you can fake it with really thin tet meshes.

